        <h3>Purpose</h3>
        <p>
            The STEM Student Scholars Program shall promote excellence
            in knowledge, skills and ability of a select group of STEM students        
            to ensure their success in securing research internships and successful             
            transfer to their targeted 4-year institution.
        </p>
    </div>
    <div class="box-content">
        <h3>Program Elements</h3>
        <p class="lead">Academic</p>
        <p class="lead">Research</p>
        <p class="lead">Service</p>
                   
    </div>

</div>
<div class="box-2">
    <div class="box-content">
        <h4>
            Eligibility Requirements
        </h4>
        <ol>
            <li>STEM degree seeking</li>
            <li>Finished 12 college level credits with no additional remediation required</li>
            <li>Minimum 3.750 Cumulative GPA</li>
        </ol>

        <h4>
        Admission Requirements
        </h4>
        <ol>
            <li>Attended one information session</li>
            <li>Maintained minimum 3.750 Cumulative GPA at end of Spring 2017 semester</li>
            <li>Completed and submitted a 3SP application</li>
            <li>Joined a 3SP Faculty Research Mentorâ€™s project team for Summer I or Summer II internship</li>
            <li>Will remain a Bergen student through the fall 2017 semester</li>
        </ol>
